{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"1. Wee voor de lasteraars (de roddelaars), degenen die kwaadspreken (door de fouten op te zoeken van hun broeders en nog veel erger; bij de mensen van kennis).","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun likulli humazatin lumazatin ","translations":["Woe","to every","slanderer","backbiter","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","likulli","humazatin","lumazatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1860],[3,1860,2810],[4,2810,4535]]}},{"name":"104:2","price":"2. Die de rijkdom verzamelt en deze telt.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī jamaʿa mālan waʿaddadahu ","translations":["The one who","collects","wealth","and counts it","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","jamaʿa","mālan","waʿaddadahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,1830],[3,1830,2950],[4,2950,5305]]}},{"name":"104:3","price":"3. Hij denkt dat hij door deze rijkdom voor altijd zal bestaan!","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"yaḥsabu anna mālahu akhladahu ","translations":["Thinking","that","his wealth","will make him immortal","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["yaḥsabu","anna","mālahu","akhladahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2410],[3,2410,4890],[4,4890,6575]]}},{"name":"104:4","price":"4. Nee! Waarlijk, hij zal in het verpletterende vuur gegooid worden.","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā layunbadhanna fī al-ḥuṭamati ","translations":["Nay","Surely he will be thrown","in","the Crusher","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","layunbadhanna","fī","al-ḥuṭamati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,4800],[3,4800,5090],[4,5090,6665]]}},{"name":"104:5","price":"5. En wat laat jullie weten wat het verpletterende vuur is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6184,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-ḥuṭamatu ","translations":["And what","will make you know","what","the Crusher (is)","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-ḥuṭamatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,3120],[3,3120,3310],[4,3310,4945]]}},{"name":"104:6","price":"6. Het vuur dat Allah heeft aangestoken.","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6185,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"nāru al-lahi al-mūqadatu ","translations":["A Fire","Allah","kindled","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["nāru","al-lahi","al-mūqadatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1640],[3,1640,3425]]}},{"name":"104:7","price":"7. Dat naar hun harten opspringt.","arabic":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6186,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"allatī taṭṭaliʿu ʿalā al-afidati ","translations":["Which","mounts up","to","the hearts","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["allatī","taṭṭaliʿu","ʿalā","al-afidati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,2210],[3,2210,2550],[4,2550,4315]]}},{"name":"104:8","price":"8. Waarlijk het zal hen insluiten (zoals zij ook zichzelf insloten door zondes zonder Tawbah).","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6187,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"innahā ʿalayhim mu'ṣadatun ","translations":["Indeed, it","(will be) upon them","closed over","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["innahā","ʿalayhim","mu'ṣadatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,3290],[3,3290,5585]]}},{"name":"104:9","price":"9. In pilaren die zich uitstrekken.","arabic":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6188,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"fī ʿamadin mumaddadatin ","translations":["In","columns","extended","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","ʿamadin","mumaddadatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1100],[3,1100,4865]]}}],"chapter":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah","Chapter Al-Humazah","Humazah","Surah Humazah","Chapter Humazah","Al Humazah","Surah Al Humazah","Chapter Al Humazah","Surah 104","Chapter 104","The Traducer","الهمزة"],"version":{"key":"dutch_center","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"nl","version":"2.0.4","last_update":1710543568,"title":"Dutch translation","description":"Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur’an into the Dutch language, for the Dutch Islamic Center - in progress."}}